ering Java and Scala integration**\n\nI'm thinking about whether methods could be public to simplify things, or if a nested class should be package-private. I wonder if the method return type is accessible. I need to import library classes in Java and question if Java will compile if I import private Scala classes directly. This might help avoid reflection and keep direct class references, which is important for the Native Image. I plan to edit the Scala test to remove reflection.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_08953fcd1000c0ed0169fa71c41c10819d8fc5c2f1c6fdf703\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp-nHZiPcqP8AOkdqWErezM08u3wcQ1E5PBGFCiCTjmpFJmpR1lEhUDqCw0HZxxVlAqcejPNosA57W0wvCa_4CDBvXiFv6yQk4Rh8A7LV73hMbQZbub21shQW_-0jZv9wKV-AKwEHEhf-4RtzeTGsV1G3phWZpEo_2-F0MYEwpNhVeG2C_s_wr7xqvq-AbWmEiQxpzO2OBVISpZTnC8clGfJGyyd-E1Waw19_Wr9f-Hg5SixBrlQIQ6dv_EsmQRFPpJ6aN66BwaAGgMnoo6bigkip-ZvzlzWUPri82tpxBX7vKonFEjKULS_0bHYk4UCjp6w8znPC6fbUiwA-9Ap-IqETGXKxoLTRV6e4-JJp1j--tUvzGz-QjP3JQoJcEiN6rjn5eGHSSY_mHegPdRJsQFqml2qMP3Drmr8Rswn2GJ8GRbHGWhsCg3guNr995cDX1ceb5u4KqZHfWWNex0OK9KUZIcdpz38B85fDEi6aGDnjLoTYybDvNURqo_ig0k8GqMlTj4O7BZPy79894_CY3l6o2pHOebzO3cCPoVUuSR9-NK9dbcWHm5OyuhLmkqRg5_Y_nW14hxarCS206hFZIBf0ZCJ7UwZtPvnIomHFTkYqKsJLNcqgjzg6hySbOwMRGGwK5f796tuGQUoYP3xMNEN51iIP7iWuNShedfgVSSrDRQUGEB8oeXRwr3dD2ePf0WQXMFeCYFdc1_rJmfG-IMvDaTrHmeLoLtLy2VXjwieWLMzdNdL-gX4aK6MSkfpnCpsab3gmFmKt2NQz8Ty5EiXaBHd1e03Ocpk9OHgcI7cV5dn5Gi5L-dkC3DceJ2YiO8QESTibNPfBSQYiyJD7-3Qk2Z6uXmD0oxhzrL9h78LTbJ5hnhfv-y2IvH2ndvgFDxTjte0kh92rYSVBAVD2R6t1Hl8KuD8wy9f44bQXywv9mu4opOSrq4ir6qAPO5h6Byg0Ac9_voQhZ6DXGzAmKgtW72JfUOUA_4SbOJyzu1BYrxdEjp2gF1xBmIzckP89tbFF46v-BoFLQ8jeEcT7MnQcpoZaN5k9GbJTIW3ebEraasm61zONYqwpR_6rpIsajllXqgpXRtcgeDiZpiYg8zmOnTyyDoe6rStqUZDD3GzVsFpumq6OA5zd3NKqdSYsKMt32t1rOnsPpRLk1XzCucYCWaZPyzePG3wpoBp9kCWHRGInCl8S2W52WHucX8PRlp5XsJFFfcXHdiSluX4lYtDKpfjxTZf0CYg_MfHnbQ4N6PGMO7vXONvbsfYrlqdZ0yQ3J17njN-_5GXzrIBNyh5dlNS4OVXoe7dt6eFLPCzAngHPcPeKRvME2L4GWAq0OhPZRRzmcsoKPAJjs5gCxoaWSY